name: Water/Liquid Girls (Element) by YeiyeiArt
description:
This model is a continuation of the series (elements) where we can make incredible elemental girls, its one of my favorite works. Basically it transforms your characters into Water in a more exaggerated way, unlike using only prompts. The model is mostly trained with images of girls, so it will be easier to create water girls.

It has not been tested on objects but I think it could work. I recommend using Lora with forces from (1.0 - 0.4).

If you want a more loquid and clean body I recommend using the following keywords (Fullwater), and also works (girl by Fullwater) for greater precision. Additionally use the following keywords to get a better water body: (liquid body, liquid, water, blue skin: 1). use the last number to manipulate the weight” ENJOY!!! :DD

Last Element --> (Fire girl).

CHECK THE OTHER LORAS!!!
